com.ashtonit.odb.realm

Class OdbPrincipal

  • Object
    • org.apache.catalina.realm.GenericPrincipal
      • com.ashtonit.odb.realm.OdbPrincipal
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Principal, TomcatPrincipal

    public class OdbPrincipal
extends GenericPrincipal
    This class extends GenericPrincipal and also contains a dbUrl property, the value of which must be the URL of the OrientDB database. The name, password and dbUrl properties can be used to instantiate an OrientGraph instance or obtain one through the pool. If you use OdbFilter you should not need to use this class anywhere else.
    Author:
    Bruce Ashton
